column5: That was very brave. Be proud of yourself.
I am sorry to hear about what you went through. I hope you are safe now.
I stand with you 100%. You did what was necessary. Now I hope you have safer days ahead.
I am so sorry to hear about your experience. Please don't harm yourself, it is not your fault. Are you still in danger? Is there any close friend who you can move in with or confide in?
Whoa, that is fucked. I hope he doesn't come back.
I am sorry you had to deal with sickos like that. I hope that it's smooth sailing from here for you.
You're not alone, I've often worried about the vulnerable young ones here. I being 25 myself and having had my fair share of run ins with predators over the years. Try and stay safe everyone.

I am so sorry to hear that. First off it is not your fault. It is solely on him. Is there a trusted adult you can confide in? I would suggest that you document it as best you can and tell someone who can help you get to a safe place.
I work in grocery and am often fatigued, you essentially boost my morale.
It is not your fault he is hitting you. That is solely on him. Document any and everything, I would recommend going to the authorities about it.
I am so sorry to hear that. I hope you are safe and well now.
I am so sorry that they did that. They were obviously not worth your time and didn't deserve you.
I love your hair and slayer shirt. I'm a big Danzig fan myself.

I understand completely. From a male element however. I have to be the strongest, smartest, etcetera. I never ask for help, I have been able to get to show my vulnerable side to a couple of people, but it wasn't easy. It never is. It doesn't help that my brother and dad act like they are Hercules. I'm learning how to heal myself, I find meditating helps but it might not be for everyone.
I am sorry. If you ever need to get the thoughts out of your head, I'm open to listening. Have you ever given thought to telling her?
Thank you for sharing your journal entry.

I feel the exact same way. Last one I was with did stop bothering with me after I told her, she was pushy for sex and I told her that made me uncomfortable, then for a couple weeks after she would make "I'll have sex with you whether you want to or not" kind of jokes and comments. I actually haven't spoken to her or have seen her in months.
No, I am serious. Every race, culture and religion has suffered at the hands of another. Human history proves that.

Actually white people have experienced racism, all races are equal in the hardships they've endured. Be it slavery, genocide or simple name calling. No one should have to be subjected to anything because of colour or beliefs. And to wish "white people got a taste of their own medicine" is no different than a white person wishing bad harm on a black person or a Latino wishing harm on an Asian. We are all one race. With any luck this virus will clear out humans making way for the superior animal, Dogs. Haha.
I am so sorry that you suffered that. If you need to vent I am here for you to chat.
No problem, if you ever need to vent my DM is always open.

I love your tattoo
Happy birthday, I hope it is well.

First off I want to say thank you for your service during the pandemic. It must be an incredibly hard time to get through. I am always open to chat about anything, if you just want to vent steam I am always willing to listen. I hope you are well.
Thank you for your kind sympathies.
Thank you for your kind words. I hope you are well.
I read your story and I am sorry you had to go through that. But we are both here, both safe. None of us are alone.
Thank you very much. It's still hard to talk about but one step at a time right.
Thank you for saying that. I appreciate your sympathy and I hope you are safe and well.

Thank you for your well wishes. I hope you are well. The area I live in is crap for mental health care especially for sex abuse/assault victims. But I'll keep looking for a professional or at least a peer support group.
Physical sense I am safe and secure but mentally and emotionally I am still kind of messed. But I am getting better. Thank you for your concern.
Hi, how are you? Did you want to chat privately?
Nice. Do you enjoy baking?
Stews are the best. I also enjoy Asian cuisine. Had some Indian years ago but it wasn't for me.

What do you like to sing? I find with myself it is a medley of things like metal, blues, folk. What resonates with you? I play guitar as well, do you play any instruments? I'm a 25 year old male by the way.

I loved it, his performance was brilliant. I just saw it a second time. I love the line "you just stay here and be u..seless."
Her son and husband deserve a brutal shit kicking. I hope that while in prison he suffers the same fear and psychological trauma he put her through.
I've waited for so long to cumtribute mommy.
How do you not have legions waiting to satisfy your every need? If you ever need a young fellow to help you, just beckon me over.
It is true. We all feel like that sometimes, we all still feel like that scared and vulnerable kid. But we have grown. We have scars, but we survived. We will survive.
Please keep fighting, if for nothing else than to spite them. If you give up, if you stop existing they win. Do not give them one inch, you are a survivor, you are strong.
